&lt;p&gt;Let&amp;#39;s summarize the changes we made:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We changed the code to iterate over the list of todos&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We tweaked the code to disallow duplicate todos in the datastore (unplanned changed, but a good one).  Also unplanned, we added a check to make sure the request contained a list of todos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We changed the request model to accept a list of todos&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We updated the specification&amp;#39;s request model definition &lt;em&gt;and description&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And now we can test it out:&lt;/p&gt;
